[proxy:0:0@fre0123] HYDU_create_process (utils/launch/launch.c:73): execvp error on file write_append_truncate (No such file or directory)
 ...
[proxy:0:1@fre0124] HYDU_create_process (utils/launch/launch.c:73): execvp error on file write_append_truncate (No such file or directory)
 parallel-scale test_write_append_truncate: @@@@@@ FAIL: write_append_truncate failed! 
&lt;/pre&gt;
